00:31:31.490 --> 00:31:33.620
its-- the limitations of its past,

00:31:33.650 --> 00:31:39.540
and moving forward in time.
Then we have reasons to hope that--

00:31:39.570 --> 00:31:43.980
what the greatness
of beings, that we see in

00:31:44.010 --> 00:31:45.540
Tulkus, into intimate dialogue

00:31:45.570 --> 00:31:49.500
with Termas,
is something that all of humanity

00:31:49.530 --> 00:31:54.064
is aspiring to, and all
of humanity can become.

